section:
&reftitle.install;
Use --with-pdo-cassandra[=FILE] to install the PDO Cassandra extension, where the optional [=FILE] is the path to thrift interfaces file. Additional configuration options --with-thrift-dir[=DIR] and --with-boost-dir[=DIR] can be used to specify thrift and boost installation prefixes.
$ ./configure --with-pdo-cassandra[=FILE] [--with-thrift-dir[=DIR] --with-boost-dir[=dir]]
